title: Portfolio
text:
This is a template for a personal portfolio site built using Quarto.
My name is Axel Zweistra, I am a graduate student of methods & statistics at Utrecht University. My master thesis focuses on developing structural equation model specifications that utilize random intercepts to correct for time-varying confounding.

title: Contact
text: You can contact me at my Github page or send me an e-mail at a.p.zweistra@uu.nl.
